  "verified_claims": [
    "A new nontrivial HB39 operator Omega_HB has been constructed from the two previously kernel-obstructed annular rotations after half-braiding projection and identity stabilization.",
    "The full tube-pair operator is represented in factored form Phi_Omega = S R_Omega P, so it preserves the full 44,224-dimensional projection kernel exactly.",
    "The induced closed-loop quotient action R_Omega is invertible on the 297-dimensional quotient.",
    "The induced action on the 39 Drinfeld primitive sectors is nontrivial, non-diagonal, and invertible.",
    "This is an adjoined quotient/HB operator, not a raw annular permutation and not yet a completed modular S,T datum."
